Actors:
1. Customer - End user who orders food
2. Restaurant - Food provider managing menu and orders
3. Delivery Driver - Person delivering the food

Use Cases:
1. Browse Menu - Customer views available food items
2. Place Order - Customer selects items and creates order
3. Make Payment - Customer pays for the order
4. Track Delivery - Customer and Driver monitor delivery status
5. Manage Menu - Restaurant updates food items and prices
